Detailed Description

cvmx_gmx::_tx::_stat1

GMX_TX_STAT1 = GMX_TX_STATS_SCOL / GMX_TX_STATS_MCOL

Notes:

  • Cleared either by a write (of any value) or a read when GMX_TX_STATS_CTL[RD_CLR] is set
  • Counters will wrap
